Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:36.90,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,Never in my life I will put out this beaconing light
Comment: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:48.00,Lyrics kanji,,0,0,0,,忘れないわあかねの朝に 誓ったことば
