Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:48.00,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,I will not misrecollect
Comment: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:56.97,Lyrics kanji,,0,0,0,,若葉にそまる 春を呼ぼうと
