Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:56.97,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,With the voices of new leaves, the spring is summoned
Comment: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:08.86,Lyrics kanji,,0,0,0,,斧うつひびき 道ひらくうたごえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:08.86,Lyrics romaji,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:03.06,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,The sounds of axes chopping trees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:08.86,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,is a song rumbling on the broad roads
Comment: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:20.74,Lyrics kanji,,0,0,0,,こだまが胸に はずんでくるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:20.74,Lyrics romaji,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:15.11,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,The chest trembles in blissful ease,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:20.74,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,echoing with mountain peaks
Comment: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:26.58,Lyrics kanji,,0,0,0,,このおお空の 虹になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:26.58,Lyrics romaji,,0,0,0,,Kono oozora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:26.58,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,In this sky of endless blue I want to be a rainbow too
