Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:36.38,Lyrics romaji,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:36.38,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,To be reaching for the hope, I want to become a rainbow
